<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Us | MatundaAfyaKenya</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #28a745;
      --secondary: #f4f4f4;
      --text-color: #333;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--secondary);
      color: var(--text-color);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 1.5em 1em;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2em;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 2em 1em;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 2em;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5em;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    h2 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }

    .grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2em;
    }

    .grid > div {
      flex: 1 1 300px;
    }

    .highlight {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 1em;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 1em;
    }

    .values-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .values-list li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1em;
      background-color: #eee;
      margin-top: 2em;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header h1 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h4>About MatundaAfyaKenya</h4>
    <p>Fresh Fruits Delivered with Care Across Kenya</p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section>
      <h4>Who We Are</h4>
      <p>MatundaAfyaKenya is a Kenyan-based fruit delivery company that connects customers to the freshest, healthiest fruits grown by trusted local farmers. We believe in quality, convenience, and nutrition—delivered right to your doorstep.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <div>
        <h4>Our Mission</h4>
        <p>To promote healthy living by making fresh fruits accessible to every household in Kenya, while supporting local agriculture and sustainable farming practices.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Our Vision</h4>
        <p>To become Kenya’s most reliable and loved fruit delivery brand, known for quality produce, fair prices, and excellent customer service.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h4>Our Values</h4>
      <ul class="values-list">
        <li>✅ Freshness First – We only deliver premium quality, farm-fresh fruits.</li>
        <li>✅ Customer Commitment – Your satisfaction is our priority.</li>
        <li>✅ Local Support – We empower local farmers and communities.</li>
        <li>✅ Eco-Friendly – Our packaging is reusable and biodegradable.</li>
        <li>✅ Reliability – Orders delivered on time, every time.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h4>Meet the Team</h4>
      <p>Behind MatundaAfyaKenya is a passionate team of nutritionists, logistics experts, and friendly customer service representatives all working together to make your fruit experience seamless and enjoyable.</p>
      <div class="highlight">
        <strong>Need help or have questions?</strong><br />
        Email us at <a href="mailto:support@matundaafyakenya.co.ke" style="color: white; text-decoration: underline;">support@matundaafyakenya.co.ke</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> MatundaAfyaKenya. All rights reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
